                        <interp inst="t18430227-1091-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 17.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.—<rs id="t18430227-1091-punishment-232" type="punishmentDescription">
